{"tid":959684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我要有抑鬱？","createTime":"2018-12-28T19:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T10:38:50.000Z","uid":151221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b55ae8729beb1875fea22141ebc386a1a79ee5","tid":959684,"uid":151221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T19:44:31.000Z","msg":"由唔知幾時開始就發現左自己缺乏左開心嘅能力，個腦好似完全唔受自己控制咁，係咁浮現一啲我唔想再諗返起嘅負面情緒同回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都好想搵朋友傾，好想po上社交媒體將所有野抒發出黎。但係因為發作嘅次數太多又唔想嚇走曬身邊嘅朋友，而且大家平時都有好多唔開心嘅事，我唔值得再咁樣放負去影響其他在乎我嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以只可以收埋係自己個心度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但最近我發現我真係覺得越來越辛苦，每次唔開心嘅時候都好暈好想嘔，思維好混亂，我好怕我會日後會更加辛苦<br />\n多謝大家睇完我9up，講曬出黎終於舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661e006e276f33722a125d0190e4c59c4bac6a12","tid":959684,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"我都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n黎緊轉下環境睇下有無好啲"},{"pid":"aabf5a8f8dafc8e2d7c1a1aee8cb4a469f2a2ada","tid":959684,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T19:50:21.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"ec02e9e4fa0f0538d921ce52ea9e43f891c2037d","tid":959684,"uid":151221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661e006e276f33722a125d0190e4c59c4bac6a12","tid":959684,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"我都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n黎緊轉下環境睇下有無好啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T19:51:56.000Z","msg":"加油啊！<br />\n希望你之後會搵得返開心嘅感覺"},{"pid":"0890690229f3978d1119e474d5d8add373393d27","tid":959684,"uid":89605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aabf5a8f8dafc8e2d7c1a1aee8cb4a469f2a2ada","tid":959684,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T19:50:21.0